ults represent a first step in the\nrevision of the local gas distribution and Galactic structure and offer a new,\nbroader context to studies on the transformation of molecular gas into stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2020 19:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-27"}
