0 Gpc/h)^3\nresolved with ~10^12 resolution elements. The Websky maps and halo catalog are\npublicly available at mocks.cita.utoronto.ca/websky.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2020 19:59:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-14"}
