grain ($grey$) dust,\nwhich is known to be almost undetectable, except for the effect of dimming\nremote extragalactic sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Jan 2020 11:18:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2020 13:57:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-27"}
